headline: DTE Energy connects customers to new, expanded energy assistance dollars as cold weather returns to Michigan
summary: As temperatures begin to drop, DTE Energy (NYSE:DTE) is stepping up to help Michigan families stay safe and warm this winter. Through its Low-Income Self-Sufficiency Plan (LSP), eligible customers can access affordable, fixed monthly payments and up to $3,000 in past-due balance forgiveness. To qualify, applicants must be DTE customers and meet income guidelines.
